.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
*.suo
*.user

# ── node_modules + lib are intentionally committed ───────────────────────────
# This add-on lives directly in %APPDATA%\Local\addons\ and is used without
# an install step. Committing node_modules/ and lib/ means a fresh clone
# (or copy) is immediately runnable by Local without running `npm install`
# or `npm run build`.
#
# Uncomment the lines below if you adopt a CI pipeline that builds from source:
# node_modules/
# lib/
